                            <comment id="136527" author="ys" created="Wed, 16 Dec 2015 13:18:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this issue was caused by osd_ldiskfs_mount rpm doesn&apos;t install successful. Looks like TEI-4075 dedicate for this situation and Charlie has some idea to fix it. But i am not found the log he pasted in ticket. So Charlie could you please point us what is exactly cause for this issue?&lt;/p&gt;
